# Bluetooth SIG spec PDFs referenced by docs/BT-COMPLIANCE.md §0 but not
# redistributable (Bluetooth SIG copyright). Place locally for citation
# verification; do not commit. Expected layout (per-profile subdirs):
#
#   docs/spec/AVRCP 1.3/  — primary wire target
#     AVRCP_SPEC_V13.pdf, ESR07_ESR_V10.pdf,
#     AVRCP.ICS.p17.pdf, AVRCP.IXIT.1.6.0.pdf
#   docs/spec/AVCTP 1.2/  — paired with AVRCP 1.3 per §6 + ESR07 §2.1
#     AVCTP_SPEC_V12.pdf, AVCTP.ICS.p10.pdf, AVCTP.TS.p12.pdf
#   docs/spec/A2DP 1.3/   — audio profile triad
#     A2DP_SPEC_V13.pdf, ESR08_V1.0.0.pdf
#   docs/spec/AVDTP 1.3/  — A2DP transport
#     AVDTP_SPEC_V13.pdf, AVDTP.ICS.p14.pdf, AVDTP.TS.p23.pdf,
#     Erratum_23224_Update_Conformance_Section.pdf
#   docs/spec/GAVDP 1.3/  — A2DP role coordinator
#     GAVDP_SPEC_V13.pdf, GAVDP.ICS.p12.pdf, GAVDP.TS_.p8.pdf,
#     Erratum_23224_Update_Conformance_Section.pdf
#
# Source: https://www.bluetooth.com/specifications/specs/
docs/spec/

